## Step 7: NUF Scoring Matrix

| Idea | New | Useful | Feasible | Total | Rank | Notes |
|------|------|--------|---------|-------|------|------|
| Lost & Found System | 3 | 5 | 5 | 13 | 1 | Very useful and easy to build |
| School Announcement System | 3 | 5 | 5 | 13 | 2 | Helps students receive updates quickly |
| Student Attendance System | 3 | 5 | 4 | 12 | 3 | Useful but needs data management |
| Online Food Ordering System | 3 | 4 | 4 | 11 | 4 | Convenient but requires order processing |
| Campus Navigation App | 4 | 4 | 3 | 11 | 5 | Helpful for new students but map integration is needed |
| Library Book Search System | 2 | 4 | 4 | 10 | 6 | Useful but similar systems already exist |
